  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the cubed cassava root and cook until golden brown, about 5 minutes on each side.",
    "Stir in the chopped onion and minced garlic. Cook for an additional 2-3 minutes until softened.",
    "Fold in the red pepper flakes and season with salt and ground black pepper to taste.",
    "Sous-vide the mixture at 140°F (60°C) for about 1 hour or until cassava is tender.",
    "Remove from sous-vide machine and stir gently. Serve hot."
